      • variantToBeEdited

        void variantToBeEdited(Report referenceVariant,
                       ReportDto reportDto,
                       java.lang.String executorToken)
                throws ServerCallFailedException
        Called just before the edits in a variant are going to be saved.
        Parameters:
        referenceVariant - the original, not yet saved report. This shows the current state of the report in the database.
        reportDto - the report with the changes. This is going to be merged to after this hook is called.
        executorToken - the executor token.
        Throws:
        ServerCallFailedException
